---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Close 10Botics Tutor Access | 關閉導師應用程式存取權"
  description="How a 10Botics tutor can request closure of app access."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Close your 10Botics Tutor access</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">關閉你的 10Botics Tutor 存取權</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mt-10">
      <p>
        10Botics Tutor is a business application for tutors and other service providers working
        with 10Botics Ltd. You may request that your app access be closed at any time.
      </p>
      <p>
        10Botics Tutor 是供與 10Botics Ltd 合作的導師及其他服務供應者使用的業務應用程式。
        你可隨時要求關閉應用程式存取權。
      </p>

      <h2>What closure means / 關閉帳戶的意思</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Your tutor record will be marked retired and you will no longer be able to sign in or access lessons and opportunities.／你的導師紀錄會被標記為停用，並不能再登入或存取課堂及教學機會。</li>
        <li>Pending applications may be withdrawn or cancelled where appropriate.／尚未處理的申請可能會按情況被撤回或取消。</li>
        <li>Closure does not cancel obligations, payments, agreements or assignments already incurred.／關閉帳戶不會取消已產生的責任、付款、協議或課堂安排。</li>
        <li>10Botics will retain business records reasonably required for contractual, payment, accounting, tax, insurance, safeguarding, dispute, security and legal purposes.／10Botics 會保留因合約、付款、會計、稅務、保險、保障、爭議、安全及法律用途而合理需要的業務紀錄。</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to request closure / 如何提出要求</h2>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:info@10botics.com?subject=10Botics%20Tutor%20account%20closure%20request">info@10botics.com</a>
        from the Google email address used to sign in. Use the subject “10Botics Tutor account closure request”
        and include your full name. We may ask you to verify your identity before processing the request.
      </p>
      <p>
        請使用登入應用程式的 Google 電郵地址，電郵至
        <a href="mailto:info@10botics.com?subject=10Botics%20Tutor%20account%20closure%20request">info@10botics.com</a>，
        主旨填寫「10Botics Tutor account closure request」，並提供你的全名。
        我們在處理要求前可能會要求你核實身份。
      </p>

      <p>
        For information about personal data, retention and your access or correction rights,
        read the <a href="/tutor-app/privacy">10Botics Tutor Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        有關個人資料、保留安排及查閱或更正權利，請參閱
        <a href="/tutor-app/privacy">10Botics Tutor 私隱政策</a>。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
